imdb.plot outline: This very special kind of walk through follows the zany misadventures of iconic and three dimensional characters as they love, lose, lick, and smash in the fantasy world of Skyrim. Different characters are followed from season to season, but all of the characters are part of the same story and exist in the same universe.
